<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.7">
<l>pappa vappar mūtta vāṟu pāḻppa tucīttiraḷai</l>
<l>yoppa vaikkaḷ pōta vunta vuṉtamark kāṇmiṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>ceppu nērmeṉ koṅkai nallār tāmci riyātamuṉṉam</l>
<l>vaippum naṅkaḷ vāḻvu māṉāṉ vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before ladies with soft breasts like copper pots can laugh [at me]</l>
<l>Saying, “Ugh! The way that old man ages is a waste!</l>
<l>Look at your clansman as he profusely hacks up phlegm like globs of pus,”</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī him who is our life and treasure.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
